2013-12-30|2014-01-05.description: Oscar Blute betrayed Jen, took her children and left her for dead. Now, Oscar's violent, brutal past is unveiled as he flees America and makes his way to the Blute family home in Europe, where his past is waiting to catch up with his future.
2013-12-30|2014-01-05.name: Blood Legacy 4: Overly Sanguine

2013-01-21|2013-01-27.description: "Return of Batman" part 1! When WayneTech's stock prices fall, Batman must fight crime...on a budget. Will his ability to fend off Ra's al Ghul and his minions suffer?
2013-01-21|2013-01-27.name: Return of Batman, Part 1 of 4

2013-02-11|2013-02-17.description: A speed storm is about to hit Vegas with the Black Flash in the middle of it all. Lives are at risk and Superman's bound to stop it, but first he's going to have to get--a new suit? Original Flash Jay Garrick lends support and advice, while elsewhere, events continue to unfold on Earth 2.
2013-02-11|2013-02-17.name: Haunted Part 8

2013-02-25|2013-03-03.description: New father Prophet survives an assassination attempt while an unseen 13,000-year-old creature from Old Earth manipulates the Empire council.
2013-02-25|2013-03-03.name: [untitled]

2013-03-18|2013-03-24.description: The greatest samurai duel in the history of Japan between Miyamoto Musashi and Sasaki Kojiro draws closer as their different intertwining paths head toward their imminent conclusion. For now, Kojiro finds himself in a new position as sword instructor to the powerful Hosokawa Clan in Kokura. Meanwhile, Musashi is still dealing with the aftermath of singlehandedly destroying the mighty Yoshioka School.
2013-03-18|2013-03-24.name: Vol. 34

2013-03-18|2013-03-24.description: Sonja takes the fight to Hyrkania itself, and finishes the war where it all began. The question is, who will stand when kingdoms fall?

2013-04-01|2013-04-07.description:
Goodbye.

FINAL ISSUE. FOR NOW.

- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -

Glory goes to heaven to get her friends back to the world of those who have not died yet. She loses the chance to spend her life after death in Heaven, because of this.

When she gets there, she finds out that her friends don`t wanna go.

Glory`s reunited with someone she loved.

Then she bids goodbye to everyone, and leaves.

She, Nanaja, their sister and their parents go trod the world, search for adventures.

And in a secret location, strange, masked men discuss about the backfiring of their plan. But, it is but a minor delay. Before long, world will find out about The Prophet.
2013-04-01|2013-04-07.name: The End

2013-04-08|2013-04-14.description: Welcome to Century City, the home of the Green Hornet! The new Green Hornet has the support of the police and City Hall and the people love him. Will that be enough to stop a terrorist group bent on detonating a dirty bomb? The new Green Hornet may need a new partner!

2013-04-15|2013-04-21.description:
The Symbiote Slayers are here. You read that correctly.

Toxin. Venom. Bunn. Shalvey. War.
2013-04-15|2013-04-21.name: Family Bonding

2013-04-15|2013-04-21.description: Ba'alzamon, the Great Lord of the Dark, has finally found the one he's looking for - Rand - and they finally meet, face to face... It's the penultimate chapter of Robert Jordan's masterpiece, The Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World!

volume.name: Robert Jordan's Wheel of Time: The Eye of the World

2013-05-27|2013-06-02.description: When a pilot gets in deep with the wrong kind of people, the Starling City vigilante becomes an unlikely ally in the fight to save his family.
2013-05-27|2013-06-02.name: You Owe Me

2013-06-03|2013-06-09.description: When an alien abducts an important public figure and the Mystery Machine, it's up to Scooby and the gang to crack the case and get their wheels back!
2013-06-03|2013-06-09.name: The Case of the Hi-Fi E.T.s

2013-07-15|2013-07-21.description:
In Astro Boy: Ivan the Fool, Astro Boy discovers the truth behind the huge monster that seems to be rampaging around the moon, and it's far different from what he expected! As it turns out, other people have been to the far side of the moon before him! Also included are Buddha, Adolf, and Black Jack.

Story Titles

  • Astro Boy: Ivan the Fool Chapter Two
  • Buddha Part Three: The Ordeals
  • Adolf: An Exile In Japan Chapter Five
  • Black Jack: A Woman's Case
2013-07-15|2013-07-21.name: Vol. 34

2013-08-05|2013-08-11.description:
Amanda is lost. Her strength came from the insanity she embraced but when the Crossed take the companions of Base M from her, she slides into a misery laced schizophrenia that threatens to destroy her as surely as the infected. With visions of Lorre haunting her and a tribe of freakishly religious Crossed on the rampage, she slips down a dangerous slope into a desperate state. And when survivors find her, they think she is one of them, but she's far worse than they can imagine. DAVID LAPHAM has once again unleashed a horrific story that will leave you scarred forever.

Available with a Regular cover by Raulo Caceres, Torture & Wraparound covers by Gabriel Andrade, and a special Red Crossed Incentive also by Caceres.

Jami the Assembler's own security protocols have trapped THE 99 members inside their own headquarters! As they struggle to defeat Jami's clever devices, Noora works to get past a murky barrier of another kind--does it hold the clue to who is behind this assault on THE 99? Find out as this house party winds down!

As they struggle to defeat Jami's clever devices, Noora works to get past a murky barrier of another kind--does it hold the clue to who is behind this assault on THE 99? Find out as this house party winds down!

2013-08-12|2013-08-18.description:
THE HELLFIRE SAGA CONCLUDES!

Wolverine and the X-Men face Mystique, Sabretooth and the Hellfire Club!

What fate awaits the Jean Grey School students who joined the New Hellions?

The WOLVERINE AND THE X-MEN landscape is redefined!
2013-08-12|2013-08-18.name: The Hellfire Saga Part Four

2013-09-02|2013-09-08.description: Batman now possesses one of Superman's super pills, but he knows his former friend is coming for him. It's a race against time to see if he can manufacture more pills and shift the balance of power.
2013-09-02|2013-09-08.name: Chapter 34

2013-09-16|2013-09-22.description: Having glimpsed a possible future, Vampirella makes a major choice for herself: she's going to become the Patron Saint of Monsters, and start by constructing a place of refuge for the weird and fearful. The road to Hell is paved with good intentions...
2013-09-16|2013-09-22.name: She Sells Sanctuary Part 1 of 2

2013-09-16|2013-09-22.description: In order to survive an all-out attack from a group of supernatural hunters, Becky Montcrief finds herself fighting side-by-side with the most unexpected of allies - the four horsemen of General Oliander Bedford Hume! Meanwhile Gord, Kirby, and Asher wage war against demonic skinwalkers and the inhuman minions of Missy Hume.
2013-09-16|2013-09-22.name: Ghost Dance, Part Five

2013-11-18|2013-11-24.description: Christmas time is here... and Santa's reindeer are on strike?!! The jolly man in red calls on his trusted assistant Archie to help get things back on track in time for the biggest night of the year. Can Archie inspire everyone to work together, or will this be a present-less holiday for children all over the world? Find out in "A Christmas Story!"
2013-11-18|2013-11-24.name: A Christmas Story

2013-12-16|2013-12-22.description: “The Demolisher” part 1 of 3! When Superman is unable to apprehend the Toyman after a frustrating encounter, a new vigilante known only as the Demolisher shows up in Metropolis. Seemingly willing to cross the lines that Superman never would, the Demolisher is quickly embraced by the people—but is he the type of hero that Metropolis truly needs?
2013-12-16|2013-12-22.name: The Demolisher Part 1 of 3

2013-12-16|2013-12-22.description:
Daredevil's become New York's most dangerous man--the self-appointed prosecutor of the Sons of the Serpent, the secret clan who owns and operates the city's justice system!

The odds are against DD--and that's just how he likes it!
